            "failure_message": "Requires a clear admiration signal plus an appreciation/focus companion (interest, inspiration, aesthetic appreciation, or quiet absorption) so the beat reads as attentive uplift rather than flat appraisal. If the actor is very comforted (deeply soothed/held), require *strong* admiration to avoid the beat misreading a comforted-vulnerability moment as admiration. Suppresses competitive or devaluing blends (envy/jealousy/resentment/cynicism, contempt/disgust), prevents a self-collapsing humbling into shame/humiliation, and blocks high threat/hostility states (fear/anxiety/hypervigilance, rage/wrath/protest/moral outrage). Triggers only on a noticeable admiration/appreciation spike to avoid repeated firing during steady admiration."
